<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<p class="p">Following empirical observations [
 <xref rid="pone.0177778.ref038" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">38</xref>], mean dispersal distance 
 <italic class="italic">δ</italic> [
 <xref rid="pone.0177778.ref052" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">52</xref>] decreases exponentially with seed mass 
 <italic class="italic">SM</italic> according to 
 <inline-formula id="pone.0177778.e005" class="inline-formula">
  <alternatives class="alternatives">
   <graphic xlink:href="pone.0177778.e005.jpg" id="pone.0177778.e005g" mimetype="image" position="anchor" orientation="portrait" class="graphic" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
   <math id="M5" class="math">
    <mrow class="mrow">
     <mi class="mi">δ</mi>
     <mo class="mo">=</mo>
     <mi class="mi">β</mi>
     <mfrac class="mfrac">
      <mrow class="mrow">
       <mo class="mo">Γ</mo>
       <mo class="mo">(</mo>
       <mn class="mn">3</mn>
       <mo class="mo">/</mo>
       <mi class="mi">c</mi>
       <mo class="mo">)</mo>
      </mrow>
      <mrow class="mrow">
       <mo class="mo">Γ</mo>
       <mo class="mo">(</mo>
       <mn class="mn">2</mn>
       <mo class="mo">/</mo>
       <mi class="mi">c</mi>
       <mo class="mo">)</mo>
      </mrow>
     </mfrac>
     <mo class="mo">=</mo>
     <mi class="mi">a</mi>
     <mo class="mo">*</mo>
     <mi class="mi">S</mi>
     <msup class="msup">
      <mi class="mi">M</mi>
      <mrow class="mrow">
       <mo class="mo">-</mo>
       <mn class="mn">0</mn>
       <mo class="mo">.</mo>
       <mn class="mn">13</mn>
      </mrow>
     </msup>
    </mrow>
   </math>
  </alternatives>
 </inline-formula>. Parameter 
 <italic class="italic">a</italic> is set to 
 <italic class="italic">a</italic> = 600 following [
 <xref rid="pone.0177778.ref053" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">53</xref>], corresponding to a mean dispersal distance of 600 m for a seed of mass 1 mg (illustrated in Fig B in 
 <xref ref-type="supplementary-material" rid="pone.0177778.s001" class="xref">S1 Appendix</xref>). From this scaling relation, the seed mass dependent species-specific dispersal parameter 
 <italic class="italic">β</italic>
 <sub class="sub">
  <italic class="italic">i</italic>
 </sub> is calculated as 
 <disp-formula id="pone.0177778.e006" class="disp-formula">
  <alternatives class="alternatives">
   <graphic xlink:href="pone.0177778.e006.jpg" id="pone.0177778.e006g" mimetype="image" position="anchor" orientation="portrait" class="graphic" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
   <math id="M6" class="math">
    <mtable displaystyle="true" class="mtable">
     <mtr class="mtr">
      <mtd columnalign="right" class="mtd">
       <mrow class="mrow">
        <msub class="msub">
         <mi class="mi">β</mi>
         <mi class="mi">i</mi>
        </msub>
        <mo class="mo">=</mo>
        <mi class="mi">a</mi>
        <mo class="mo">*</mo>
        <mfrac class="mfrac">
         <mrow class="mrow">
          <mo class="mo">Γ</mo>
          <mo class="mo">(</mo>
          <mn class="mn">2</mn>
          <mo class="mo">/</mo>
          <mi class="mi">c</mi>
          <mo class="mo">)</mo>
         </mrow>
         <mrow class="mrow">
          <mo class="mo">Γ</mo>
          <mo class="mo">(</mo>
          <mn class="mn">3</mn>
          <mo class="mo">/</mo>
          <mi class="mi">c</mi>
          <mo class="mo">)</mo>
         </mrow>
        </mfrac>
        <mo class="mo">*</mo>
        <mi class="mi">S</mi>
        <msup class="msup">
         <mi class="mi">M</mi>
         <mrow class="mrow">
          <mo class="mo">-</mo>
          <mn class="mn">0</mn>
          <mo class="mo">.</mo>
          <mn class="mn">13</mn>
         </mrow>
        </msup>
       </mrow>
      </mtd>
     </mtr>
    </mtable>
   </math>
  </alternatives>
  <label class="label">(4)</label>
 </disp-formula>
</p>
